BURY
====

Usage: bury [corpse]

Bury a corpse in the current room. All items inside the corpse are
destroyed along with it.

Examples:
  bury              - Bury the first corpse in the room
  bury wolf corpse  - Bury a specific corpse

Note: If you want to loot a corpse before burying it, use 'get' to take
items from it first. Once buried, all contents are lost forever.

See also: get, look
